      <title>Grifols 通过特殊债券条款向 Brookfield 敞开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/grifols-keeps-door-open-to-brookfield-with-special-bond-clause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Grifols SA 在其 13 亿欧元（14 亿美元）的私人债务配售中加入了一项条款，允许 Brookfield Asset Management Ltd. 提前为该交易进行再融资 — — 这表明这家西班牙制药商为这家私募股权公司采取另一种方式敞开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/grifols-keeps-door-open-to-brookfield-with-special-bond-clause</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 17:33:07 GMT</pubDate>
